      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "clarify",
      "utterance": "明白，所以起点是Retail_CouponSystem，终点是Retail_PointOfSale。中间账户会有哪些主要状态？Registered和Active肯定是有的吧？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registered",
        "Active"
