    {
      "turn_id": 3,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "对，Registered是初始状态，需要邮件或身份验证后才能变成Active。但Active不是终点，账户还可能被暂停或用户主动注销。",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registered",
        "Active",
        "Suspended",
        "Deactivated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 4,
      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "confirm",
      "utterance": "好的，我梳理一下：Registered通过验证到Active；Active可以因政策违规或付款问题到Suspended，也可以用户或管理员操作到Deactivated。Suspended能恢复吗？",
      "elements_involved": [
        "Registered",
        "Active",
        "Suspended",
        "Deactivated"
      ],
      "is_repair": false
    },
    {
      "turn_id": 5,
      "role": "Domain_Expert",
      "action_type": "propose",
      "utterance": "可以，Suspended在问题解决后能回到Active。如果用户或管理员决定不再恢复，也可以直接走向Deactivated。最后Deactivated账户会进入Retail_PointOfSale做结算处理。",
      "elements_involved": [
