      "role": "Diagram_Editor",
      "action_type": "execute",
      "utterance": "结构清楚了，我先画一版。起点Retail_CouponSystem创建账户到Registered，验证后到Active，然后分支到Suspended或Deactivated，Suspended可回退也可前进，最终Deactivated到Retail_PointOfSale。",
